definition:
Someone descended from Ishvi who was a man of the tribe of Asher living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.17; 
 son of: Asher (H0836); 
 brother of: Imnah (H3232), Ishvah (H3438), Beriah (H1283) and Serah (H8294)
Group of yish.vi (יִשְׁוִי "Ishvi" H3440) 
